    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I’m here to make sure the new arrivals understand the boundaries. Just because our gates are open to all faithful doesn’t mean they can go anywhere they please,” explains the guard.

“Of course, men of standing and reputation are welcome anywhere but those who belong at the bottom should stay at the bottom.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I thought we were all brothers and sisters.”</text>
          <def_link>4</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>3</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“In Gods’ eyes we are,” nods the guard, ignoring your sarcasm, “which doesn’t mean we shouldn’t have order. If you were dirt poor before, you won’t be sleeping on a feather bed when you come here, but you’ll pray freely and without fear.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What about the crosses?”</text>
          <def_link>5</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“It’s the Holy City,” says the guard, giving you a long, hard look as if finally finding you worthy of his full attention. “If you aren’t a &lt;man/woman&gt; of faith, why are you here?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I am, brother. I was merely curious who dispenses justice in Lowtown.”</text>
          <def_link>7</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“I have business here.”</text>
          <def_link>6</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>5</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Don’t overstay your welcome.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts>
